<plot>Is it a typical love triangle story: George, Martha, and the Pugs? Or a political story: George and Martha and The Gang of Three (Pugs)? Or a tragedy: Oedipus Pugs? Or none of the above? Our trilogy, in the style of Jacques Tati, has the non-feminist George struggling for his "rightful" place in the family only to find he ranks after the pugs in Martha's heart. He takes his revenge and prevails. Or does he?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?576994</url></doc>
